1
00:00:13,540 --> 00:00:15,780
♪Trap my frame♪

2
00:00:15,980 --> 00:00:20,060
♪Plagues demand I bow in shame♪

3
00:00:20,780 --> 00:00:22,940
♪Snare my soul♪

4
00:00:23,020 --> 00:00:27,100
♪Rules command I swallow my pride♪

5
00:00:27,260 --> 00:00:30,620
♪Mock my way♪

6
00:00:30,900 --> 00:00:34,060
♪Chained me where I must stay♪

7
00:00:34,420 --> 00:00:36,780
♪Taught me to kneel, not to speak♪

8
00:00:37,020 --> 00:00:41,220
♪And to let my life pass by in silence♪

9
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:44,100
♪But I heard the wind♪

10
00:00:44,220 --> 00:00:45,900
♪From the sea and the sky♪

11
00:00:46,180 --> 00:00:47,660
♪It said don't bend♪

12
00:00:47,780 --> 00:00:49,820
♪Bow your head, and your chains begin♪

13
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:51,380
♪You are the wave♪

14
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:53,300
♪And the wind that won't behave♪

15
00:00:53,380 --> 00:00:56,340
♪How could you be chained?♪

16
00:00:56,740 --> 00:00:58,740
♪Untamed, uncaged, unclaimed♪

17
00:00:58,780 --> 00:01:00,540
♪You're the blade in my gaze♪

18
00:01:00,620 --> 00:01:02,420
♪This world will leave you no space♪

19
00:01:02,500 --> 00:01:04,220
♪Then pierce it with your blaze♪

20
00:01:04,220 --> 00:01:06,100
♪My silent grind♪

21
00:01:06,100 --> 00:01:08,060
♪My aching pain♪

22
00:01:08,060 --> 00:01:10,300
♪Will one day turn...♪

23
00:01:11,860 --> 00:01:14,620
♪I am who I am♪

24
00:01:14,620 --> 00:01:18,140
♪My greatest ambition♪

25
00:01:18,220 --> 00:01:21,300
♪If the world can't contain me♪

26
00:01:21,380 --> 00:01:24,940
♪Then I'll break through it♪

27
00:01:25,420 --> 00:01:26,940
♪Become who I am♪

28
00:01:26,940 --> 00:01:28,260
[Wild Ambition Bloom]

29
00:01:28,260 --> 00:01:29,980
[Adapted from Stone and Water's novel,
The Uncaged Flame]

30
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:32,980
[Episode 18]

31
00:01:33,710 --> 00:01:34,980
Mr. Zhou,

32
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:39,210
you're finally back!

33
00:01:39,230 --> 00:01:41,380
I've waited ages for you.

34
00:01:42,070 --> 00:01:43,660
What brings you here?

35
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:46,100
I planned to wait for you at the hotel,

36
00:01:46,710 --> 00:01:48,130
but those cops didn't let me

37
00:01:48,150 --> 00:01:50,290
wait outside the entrance.

38
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:51,290
You…

39
00:01:51,310 --> 00:01:52,850
So I had no choice but to come here.

40
00:01:53,070 --> 00:01:54,540
How did you find my place?

41
00:01:54,870 --> 00:01:57,180
You're such a big shot in Shanghai now.

42
00:01:57,310 --> 00:01:58,620
Tracking down your address

43
00:01:59,310 --> 00:02:00,930
wasn't exactly hard, right?

44
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:02,900
What a beautiful house!

45
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:04,570
Come back!

46
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,130
What

47
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,690
do you want to do?

48
00:02:09,910 --> 00:02:10,780
Well, what do you think?

49
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:13,260
You're after these 50 silver dollars,
right?

50
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,170
Here they are.

51
00:02:14,190 --> 00:02:14,980
Listen to me.

52
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:17,690
Never come to me again.

53
00:02:17,870 --> 00:02:18,540
Understood?

54
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:23,290
How many people are there
in your family?

55
00:02:23,310 --> 00:02:24,130
Oh, no!

56
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,010
Here you go.

57
00:02:31,870 --> 00:02:32,610
Mark my words.

58
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:34,500
Don't ever come to me again.

59
00:02:34,870 --> 00:02:36,100
If you dare come again,

60
00:02:36,430 --> 00:02:39,850
I have plenty of ways
to make your life miserable.

61
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:40,940
Take care.

62
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,170
Got it.

63
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,610
Thanks, Mr. Zhou.

64
00:02:49,190 --> 00:02:50,780
Once it runs out,

65
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,570
I'll come to you again.

66
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:55,290
I dare you!

67
00:02:56,710 --> 00:02:57,660
Wrong way.

68
00:02:57,870 --> 00:02:59,100
Get lost!

69
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:08,340
Bai hasn't returned.

70
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,540
Anything went wrong?

71
00:03:10,030 --> 00:03:10,780
Relax.

72
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:12,780
Everything is under our control.

73
00:03:15,470 --> 00:03:16,290
I'm back.

74
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:17,290
You're back.

75
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,450
How did it go?

76
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:19,610
Success!

77
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:22,500
Dispelled all his suspicions?

78
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:23,260
I promise

79
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:24,820
he'll never want to see me again.

80
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:25,820
As long as you're fine.

81
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,540
Today's biggest success

82
00:03:27,710 --> 00:03:28,850
isn't these 50 silver dollars,

83
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:29,850
but this.

84
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:30,730
What…

85
00:03:30,750 --> 00:03:31,170
Look!

86
00:03:31,190 --> 00:03:31,850
What's this?

87
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,220
Tongxin proposed to me!

88
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:34,890
Already?

89
00:03:35,710 --> 00:03:36,610
He's a loose tongue

90
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:37,980
when he

91
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:39,260
drinks.

92
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:41,100
I seized the chance to encourage him

93
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:42,260
and he got carried away.

94
00:03:43,030 --> 00:03:44,100
So you accepted?

95
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,450
Why wouldn't I?

96
00:03:45,910 --> 00:03:47,940
I've been waiting for this day for ages!

97
00:03:59,080 --> 00:04:00,380
What's wrong with you?

98
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,100
I'm getting married!

99
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,610
Aren't you happy for me?

100
00:04:05,910 --> 00:04:06,660
Sun,

101
00:04:07,750 --> 00:04:09,690
publish a news article tomorrow

102
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:13,940
titled "Deputy General Manager
of Tian's Apothecary

103
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:16,730
Marries Film Star Bai Bingxin".

104
00:04:17,630 --> 00:04:18,290
Got it.

105
00:04:18,750 --> 00:04:19,540
It's on you then.

106
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:22,220
Aren't you going to reconsider?

107
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:23,810
Absolutely not.

108
00:04:24,270 --> 00:04:25,780
Tongxin is changing.

109
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:26,700
I must seize the chance

110
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:28,220
to nail this down once and for all

111
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:29,660
before he changes his mind.

112
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:30,730
But...

113
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:31,730
Shaohua.

114
00:04:34,270 --> 00:04:34,930
Shaohua,

115
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,100
I have a gift for you.

116
00:04:38,630 --> 00:04:39,290
Gift?

117
00:04:40,630 --> 00:04:42,020
Hurry up.

118
00:04:49,390 --> 00:04:50,250
They were collected

119
00:04:51,270 --> 00:04:53,850
by Sun through contacts in Beijing.

120
00:04:54,430 --> 00:04:55,610
Every single piece

121
00:04:55,950 --> 00:04:57,050
is about the destruction

122
00:04:57,270 --> 00:05:00,900
of Sanshou Gang.

123
00:05:01,310 --> 00:05:02,850
The bandit chief Ertu has confessed

124
00:05:03,360 --> 00:05:05,540
he killed Chen Ershun,
Ms. Zhang, his mother

125
00:05:06,270 --> 00:05:09,140
and Chen Xuan,
the family's granddaughter.

126
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:13,410
To avenge the humiliation
of being held hostage years ago,

127
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,370
he raided Huashun Apothecary

128
00:05:16,390 --> 00:05:17,460
and slaughtered the Chen family.

129
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:18,700
No.

130
00:05:19,630 --> 00:05:20,730
No.

131
00:05:20,750 --> 00:05:21,540
Shaohua.

132
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:23,700
No.

133
00:05:23,870 --> 00:05:24,540
The case is closed.

134
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:25,140
No.

135
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,140
The case is closed!

136
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:27,580
No.

137
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:30,900
All that is past.

138
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:36,460
You no longer have to worry anymore.

139
00:06:06,060 --> 00:06:08,140
[Convict of Qizhou Massacre Arrested]

140
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,850
Is she alright?

141
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:26,730
Give her some time.

142
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,020
She'll be fine.

143
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:35,050
Are you really getting married?

144
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:37,900
Not that soon.

145
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,580
Thank you very much this time!

146
00:06:44,630 --> 00:06:45,900
With what you taught me,

147
00:06:46,270 --> 00:06:47,700
I actually managed to fool them.

148
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:50,020
No problem.

149
00:06:50,190 --> 00:06:52,220
Glad you found it helpful.

150
00:06:53,430 --> 00:06:54,540
One more thing,

151
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,050
I still need your help.

152
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:58,660
Go ahead.

153
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:00,170
Keep this a secret.

154
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:02,930
Don't worry. I won't tell anyone.

155
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:05,340
Thanks.

156
00:07:09,190 --> 00:07:10,460
Don't you want to know

157
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,580
what makes Sha and I

158
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:16,050
go through

159
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:18,370
all these today.

160
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,140
Everyone has a history.

161
00:07:25,390 --> 00:07:26,900
Especially in these times,

162
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:29,580
it's been incredibly hard

163
00:07:30,270 --> 00:07:31,250
for you two to survive.

164
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,780
I understand some history

165
00:07:35,270 --> 00:07:36,100
is too painful to revisit,

166
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:37,610
and...

167
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:40,020
too raw to touch.

168
00:07:42,510 --> 00:07:43,220
Unless you share,

169
00:07:44,310 --> 00:07:45,140
I won't press.

170
00:07:46,430 --> 00:07:48,050
But whenever you need me,

171
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,460
I'll stand by you.

172
00:07:54,190 --> 00:07:55,220
Glad to have you here.

173
00:07:57,430 --> 00:07:58,900
I wish I had known you earlier.

174
00:07:59,390 --> 00:08:00,290
It's never too late.

175
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:05,580
Let's be friends forever.

176
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:11,700
Okay.

177
00:08:25,540 --> 00:08:26,400
It's all in the past now.

178
00:08:31,940 --> 00:08:32,760
At least,

179
00:08:34,820 --> 00:08:36,550
I can be Chu Shaohua again.

180
00:08:39,060 --> 00:08:39,950
That's great!

181
00:08:41,820 --> 00:08:42,550
Great!

182
00:08:44,540 --> 00:08:46,880
Glad you think this way.

183
00:08:53,660 --> 00:08:54,790
Start anew.

184
00:09:02,940 --> 00:09:03,880
By the way, Sun,

185
00:09:04,780 --> 00:09:06,760
could you help me find someone?

186
00:09:07,660 --> 00:09:08,380
No problem.

187
00:09:08,380 --> 00:09:09,280
Who do you want to find?

188
00:09:10,500 --> 00:09:13,760
Actually,  she survived that massacre

189
00:09:14,260 --> 00:09:16,790
and might still be in Qizhou.

190
00:09:17,660 --> 00:09:18,830
Her name is Song Ping.

191
00:09:23,780 --> 00:09:27,380
[Bai Bingxin Reveals Engagement
with Tian Tongxin]

192
00:09:29,300 --> 00:09:30,180
Your noodles are ready.

193
00:09:31,420 --> 00:09:32,260
Please enjoy them.

194
00:09:35,620 --> 00:09:36,500
Have you made up your mind yet?

195
00:09:38,380 --> 00:09:40,500
No need to go through all this trouble.

196
00:09:41,860 --> 00:09:42,940
Still planning to turn me down?

197
00:09:42,940 --> 00:09:44,380
No, I agree.

198
00:09:44,980 --> 00:09:46,380
I invited you out today

199
00:09:46,380 --> 00:09:47,700
just to tell you my decision.

200
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:50,980
Just pay me
according to industry standards.

201
00:09:51,550 --> 00:09:52,770
But I have one condition.

202
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:55,620
I want 10 percent
of service-based share.

203
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:56,860
What?

204
00:09:57,430 --> 00:09:58,460
You heard what I said.

205
00:09:58,780 --> 00:10:03,660
[Yangchun Noodles]

206
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:08,410
Fine.

207
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:11,770
Wen's Pharmacy welcomes you, Miss Zhu.

208
00:10:13,160 --> 00:10:14,500
Actually, my name is Chu Shaohua.

209
00:10:15,550 --> 00:10:17,140
Then why use the alias Zhu Sha?

210
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:18,500
Because it's the name of a poison.

211
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:20,530
Anyone, including demons and spirits,
touches it

212
00:10:20,670 --> 00:10:21,500
will meet their doom.

213
00:10:21,790 --> 00:10:22,770
Feeling a bit scared?

214
00:10:23,160 --> 00:10:24,140
And a touch of regret?

215
00:10:24,910 --> 00:10:25,570
Too late.

216
00:10:27,760 --> 00:10:29,140
You crafty woman!

217
00:10:30,400 --> 00:10:32,260
You were drawn by my craftiness.

218
00:10:33,160 --> 00:10:33,980
Thank you for the flowers.

219
00:10:42,590 --> 00:10:43,290
Mr. Tian,

220
00:10:43,310 --> 00:10:44,930
do you know
about Miss Bai Bingxin's engagement

221
00:10:44,950 --> 00:10:45,530
to Tian Tongxin?

222
00:10:45,790 --> 00:10:46,500
Is it true?

223
00:10:46,830 --> 00:10:47,740
What do you think about this?

224
00:10:48,670 --> 00:10:50,260
Could you grant us an interview?

225
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:51,890
Yes. Would you share a few remarks?

226
00:10:51,910 --> 00:10:52,570
Excuse me, make way.

227
00:10:52,590 --> 00:10:53,340
Please, say a few words.

228
00:11:00,590 --> 00:11:01,500
Here he comes!

229
00:11:01,880 --> 00:11:02,500
Mr. Tian!

230
00:11:02,790 --> 00:11:03,500
Mr. Tian,

231
00:11:03,520 --> 00:11:05,220
when will you and Miss Bai get married?

232
00:11:05,240 --> 00:11:06,460
Mr. Tian, will your wedding

233
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:07,570
be traditional Chinese or Western-style?

234
00:11:07,590 --> 00:11:08,220
Mr. Tian,

235
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:09,690
where have you chosen
for the wedding venue?

236
00:11:12,190 --> 00:11:12,980
Shaohua,

237
00:11:13,710 --> 00:11:14,290
look.

238
00:11:14,640 --> 00:11:16,620
Sun really went above and beyond!

239
00:11:16,880 --> 00:11:18,930
Both his own newspaper

240
00:11:19,040 --> 00:11:20,530
and his friends' carried my story!

241
00:11:20,710 --> 00:11:22,220
And all included photos. Look!

242
00:11:22,520 --> 00:11:23,100
Here.

243
00:11:23,830 --> 00:11:24,530
Here.

244
00:11:25,640 --> 00:11:26,530
Look. Photos.

245
00:11:27,040 --> 00:11:27,930
That's incredible.

246
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:30,890
Wait.

247
00:11:31,760 --> 00:11:32,770
Have you seen this?

248
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:36,290
Tian Tongxin's love life fully exposed.

249
00:11:36,310 --> 00:11:38,170
List of ex-girlfriends revealed.

250
00:11:41,670 --> 00:11:44,170
Over a dozen names are listed here.

251
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:45,140
I can't see any of them.

252
00:11:45,160 --> 00:11:46,980
All I see is my own name.

253
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:49,770
You really don't care?

254
00:11:49,950 --> 00:11:50,740
I do care.

255
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:52,810
What I care
about is whether their family has money.

256
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:56,050
Speaking of his family,

257
00:11:57,880 --> 00:12:00,650
why do both his family
and Mr. Tian himself

258
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,770
seem to avoid discussion

259
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,410
of the engagement?

260
00:12:05,670 --> 00:12:06,690
Think carefully.

261
00:12:06,710 --> 00:12:07,740
What does this mean?

262
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:10,500
It means his family doesn't approve

263
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:12,930
of this marriage.

264
00:12:13,190 --> 00:12:14,620
That's precisely

265
00:12:14,640 --> 00:12:15,980
what I expected.

266
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:18,020
Erniu,

267
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:21,260
you can't force things.

268
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:23,570
We have forced

269
00:12:23,910 --> 00:12:25,140
everything we have today, right?

270
00:12:26,640 --> 00:12:27,260
Fine.

271
00:12:28,160 --> 00:12:29,570
Since you've set your mind,

272
00:12:29,590 --> 00:12:30,690
I won't stand in your way.

273
00:12:32,070 --> 00:12:33,620
You've also decided to work
for Wen Zhiqiu?

274
00:12:35,040 --> 00:12:37,930
I quit my job
at Evernew Department today

275
00:12:38,070 --> 00:12:39,340
and told Wen Zhiqiu my decision.

276
00:12:41,070 --> 00:12:41,690
By the way,

277
00:12:42,880 --> 00:12:43,860
Ni Xiangying's been discharged
from the hospital.

278
00:12:46,160 --> 00:12:47,050
How's she doing?

279
00:12:47,950 --> 00:12:50,140
Heard her suitors won't stop coming.

280
00:12:50,520 --> 00:12:51,860
While she was hospitalized,

281
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:52,860
they sent flowers

282
00:12:52,880 --> 00:12:54,260
and gifts every day,

283
00:12:55,070 --> 00:12:56,170
but she turned everything down.

284
00:12:56,760 --> 00:12:57,340
Also

285
00:12:57,640 --> 00:12:59,340
she sent back that breakup check

286
00:12:59,520 --> 00:13:00,530
from Mr. Tian.

287
00:13:01,190 --> 00:13:02,650
Did I hear that right?

288
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:04,290
She sent everything back?

289
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:08,220
Never saw that coming, huh.

290
00:13:08,310 --> 00:13:09,650
Turns out she's got spine.

