00:26:16,240 --> 00:26:18,330
That's not important.

575
00:26:18,590 --> 00:26:19,500
What truly matters is

576
00:26:19,520 --> 00:26:21,130
that Qingshen Pill can

577
00:26:21,480 --> 00:26:22,770
better boost your good reputation

578
00:26:22,790 --> 00:26:24,420
and profits

579
00:26:24,720 --> 00:26:27,090
than the Western Bubao Pill does.

580
00:26:27,630 --> 00:26:29,290
This has to be Tongxin's doing!

581
00:26:30,440 --> 00:26:31,460
Withholding useless information

582
00:26:31,480 --> 00:26:33,530
while recklessly leaking
sensitive matters.

583
00:26:33,960 --> 00:26:34,850
So stupid!

584
00:26:37,240 --> 00:26:37,900
Sir,

585
00:26:38,720 --> 00:26:40,290
Tian's Apothecary

586
00:26:40,520 --> 00:26:42,660
has always been a role model
in the industry.

587
00:26:43,110 --> 00:26:45,090
We are deeply eager

588
00:26:45,110 --> 00:26:47,420
to collaborate with you

589
00:26:47,680 --> 00:26:49,330
to thrive both sides together.

590
00:26:49,480 --> 00:26:51,180
Also we hope Qingshen Pill
will bring relief

591
00:26:51,480 --> 00:26:53,130
and well-being to even more patients.

592
00:26:56,310 --> 00:26:58,570
You're just trying to latch
onto me, right?

593
00:27:00,960 --> 00:27:02,900
Not quite.

594
00:27:02,920 --> 00:27:04,610
Do you realize

595
00:27:04,920 --> 00:27:08,180
you are unqualified to latch onto me?

596
00:27:08,440 --> 00:27:11,570
Do you know

597
00:27:11,590 --> 00:27:13,020
who we do business with every day?

598
00:27:13,920 --> 00:27:16,330
Don't call yourself a pharmacy

599
00:27:16,590 --> 00:27:19,130
before you really are.

600
00:27:19,480 --> 00:27:21,460
We won't stock fakes

601
00:27:21,480 --> 00:27:23,530
or bad remedies here!

602
00:27:35,390 --> 00:27:37,740
Sir, would this arrangement work?

603
00:27:40,110 --> 00:27:40,770
These samples

604
00:27:41,630 --> 00:27:44,260
will stay here with you.

605
00:27:45,150 --> 00:27:48,220
Please try them personally.

606
00:27:48,630 --> 00:27:50,900
They may offer you
a different experience.

607
00:27:51,860 --> 00:27:52,700
Very well, I see.

608
00:28:00,760 --> 00:28:01,420
Mr. Tian,

609
00:28:02,150 --> 00:28:03,260
I'll take my leave then.

610
00:28:23,820 --> 00:28:26,220
[Tian's Apothecary]

611
00:28:39,390 --> 00:28:41,940
Jujing Apothecary is a rising star
in Shanghai's TCM market.

612
00:28:42,630 --> 00:28:43,980
Reportedly owned by someone
from northern.

613
00:28:44,350 --> 00:28:44,920
[Jujing Apothecary]

614
00:28:44,920 --> 00:28:46,290
It has opened six branches
in just two years,

615
00:28:47,280 --> 00:28:49,090
strategically located near every branch
of Tian's Apothecary,

616
00:28:49,480 --> 00:28:51,370
with pricing directly competing
against them.

617
00:29:00,540 --> 00:29:01,850
Madam, step right in!

618
00:29:02,110 --> 00:29:03,130
Are you not feeling well?

619
00:29:03,560 --> 00:29:04,500
We have quinine

620
00:29:04,620 --> 00:29:05,610
for malaria.

621
00:29:05,630 --> 00:29:06,810
Our plaster mends

622
00:29:06,830 --> 00:29:07,980
strained from daylight toil.

623
00:29:08,110 --> 00:29:09,020
Our Dingshen Elixir calms you

624
00:29:09,200 --> 00:29:10,370
when you suffer plague.

625
00:29:10,390 --> 00:29:11,370
Whose apothecary reigns supreme?

626
00:29:11,390 --> 00:29:12,900
Shanghai's Jujing Apothecary.

627
00:29:13,060 --> 00:29:13,770
Excuse me,

628
00:29:14,100 --> 00:29:15,900
could I meet your head manager?

629
00:29:16,590 --> 00:29:17,260
Madam,

630
00:29:17,620 --> 00:29:19,420
what can he do for you?

631
00:29:20,040 --> 00:29:22,460
I'd like to offer a prepared medicine
for sale here.

632
00:29:24,550 --> 00:29:25,530
This is my business card.

633
00:29:27,760 --> 00:29:28,850
Excuse me, Ms. Chu.

634
00:29:29,110 --> 00:29:30,260
Jujing Apothecary carries

635
00:29:30,280 --> 00:29:31,530
only our own prepared medicines.

636
00:29:33,000 --> 00:29:34,420
Please help

637
00:29:35,350 --> 00:29:36,700
ask your head manager.

638
00:29:37,590 --> 00:29:38,130
Very well.

639
00:29:38,280 --> 00:29:39,370
I'll announce your presence,

640
00:29:39,680 --> 00:29:41,180
though I'm not sure

641
00:29:41,200 --> 00:29:42,180
if he's available.

642
00:29:42,590 --> 00:29:43,980
Thank you.

643
00:29:49,310 --> 00:29:50,330
Just one dose.

644
00:29:50,960 --> 00:29:51,700
Here you are.

645
00:29:52,310 --> 00:29:53,610
Remember to take it properly.

646
00:29:54,440 --> 00:29:56,220
Also, avoid raw, cold, or spicy foods.

647
00:29:56,240 --> 00:29:56,740
Alright?

648
00:29:57,110 --> 00:29:57,900
Yes. Thanks.

649
00:29:58,280 --> 00:29:58,850
Ms. Chu,

650
00:29:59,480 --> 00:30:00,500
our manager invites you upstairs.

651
00:30:00,790 --> 00:30:01,850
That's truly wonderful!

652
00:30:02,920 --> 00:30:05,610
Oh, may I ask how to address him?

653
00:30:06,350 --> 00:30:07,260
His surname is Mei.

654
00:30:07,480 --> 00:30:08,500
But the one who will meet you

655
00:30:08,520 --> 00:30:09,940
is the big boss of Jujing Apothecary.

656
00:30:11,110 --> 00:30:11,940
Big boss?

657
00:30:12,200 --> 00:30:13,850
Yes, coincidentally, he's here today.

658
00:30:14,200 --> 00:30:15,740
Seeing your business card,
he asked to see you now.

659
00:30:17,560 --> 00:30:18,170
Please come with me.

660
00:30:18,920 --> 00:30:19,610
Alright.

661
00:30:24,200 --> 00:30:24,850
Thank you.

662
00:30:29,960 --> 00:30:30,770
Ms. Chu.

663
00:30:32,590 --> 00:30:33,290
Mr. Xia.

664
00:30:33,760 --> 00:30:34,740
So it really is you!

665
00:30:38,240 --> 00:30:39,900
Back then, I heard the Chens
were wiped out

666
00:30:40,150 --> 00:30:41,260
and you didn't escape.

667
00:30:42,440 --> 00:30:43,370
Such a tragedy!

668
00:30:44,200 --> 00:30:45,740
But it's truly delightful to see you

669
00:30:46,350 --> 00:30:47,130
safe and sound today.

670
00:30:49,440 --> 00:30:50,900
I'm also pleasantly surprised

671
00:30:51,760 --> 00:30:53,220
to see you again.

672
00:30:54,550 --> 00:30:55,260
Take a seat.

673
00:30:57,280 --> 00:30:58,460
How long have you been in Shanghai?

674
00:30:59,870 --> 00:31:02,370
Almost two years now.

675
00:31:04,310 --> 00:31:05,290
Still working with medicine?

676
00:31:06,150 --> 00:31:07,260
Yes, just can't walk away from it.

677
00:31:10,350 --> 00:31:12,460
I heard Wen's Pharmacy
has only been open for a few years.

678
00:31:13,110 --> 00:31:13,900
Not very large.

679
00:31:14,720 --> 00:31:15,220
True.

680
00:31:18,060 --> 00:31:19,100
Then no need to stoop there.

681
00:31:19,140 --> 00:31:19,620
Thanks.

682
00:31:22,140 --> 00:31:23,850
Come here and help me instead.

683
00:31:32,820 --> 00:31:33,570
To be honest,

684
00:31:34,120 --> 00:31:35,810
I hold some stocks

685
00:31:35,830 --> 00:31:39,020
in the pharmacy.

686
00:31:39,760 --> 00:31:40,810
So that explains it.

687
00:31:41,160 --> 00:31:42,050
I see.

688
00:31:43,700 --> 00:31:44,370
Ms. Chu,

689
00:31:45,340 --> 00:31:46,130
you haven't changed a bit.

690
00:31:47,020 --> 00:31:48,220
Still so ambitious.

691
00:31:53,300 --> 00:31:55,740
Perhaps the one constant in my life

692
00:31:57,260 --> 00:31:58,850
has been this very ambition.

693
00:32:01,620 --> 00:32:02,130
Alright.

694
00:32:03,380 --> 00:32:03,900
Tell me

695
00:32:04,700 --> 00:32:06,020
how you ended up coming here.

696
00:32:08,140 --> 00:32:09,050
Well...

697
00:32:13,540 --> 00:32:14,610
just a series of coincidences.

698
00:32:14,980 --> 00:32:17,570
But I believe you have come here

699
00:32:18,420 --> 00:32:20,850
with thorough preparation, huh?

700
00:32:23,940 --> 00:32:24,370
Excellent.

701
00:32:24,820 --> 00:32:26,050
Go on, share your thoughts.

702
00:32:26,420 --> 00:32:28,850
You have dominated the TCM market

703
00:32:29,020 --> 00:32:29,850
in the north.

704
00:32:30,220 --> 00:32:31,940
Now here you aim to unify

705
00:32:32,150 --> 00:32:34,540
both markets in the south and the north.

706
00:32:35,220 --> 00:32:38,300
However,
the Tian family controls the south

707
00:32:38,660 --> 00:32:41,130
with its roots in shanghai.

708
00:32:41,220 --> 00:32:43,810
Mr. Tian is narrow-minded and petty.

709
00:32:44,350 --> 00:32:45,740
So both families must have clashed

710
00:32:45,740 --> 00:32:47,090
countless times over these years.

711
00:32:50,720 --> 00:32:52,740
With your financial muscle,

712
00:32:52,760 --> 00:32:54,700
you've opened branches
and aggressively undercut prices,

713
00:32:55,110 --> 00:32:57,410
appearing to have made headway,

714
00:32:58,040 --> 00:32:58,780
yet you fail to rattle

715
00:32:59,280 --> 00:33:01,890
the Tian family's dominance here.

716
00:33:03,480 --> 00:33:05,060
At the risk of impertinence,

717
00:33:05,190 --> 00:33:07,330
what Jujing Apothecary needs now

718
00:33:07,480 --> 00:33:08,940
is an exclusive secret remedy.

719
00:33:09,350 --> 00:33:10,090
So I think

720
00:33:10,110 --> 00:33:12,090
our newly launched Qingshen Pill

721
00:33:12,910 --> 00:33:14,650
might lend a helping hand

722
00:33:14,760 --> 00:33:16,220
to Jujing Apothecary.

723
00:33:18,000 --> 00:33:19,170
See? My guess was spot-on.

724
00:33:19,760 --> 00:33:21,060
This is indeed about business.

725
00:33:21,910 --> 00:33:24,170
Yes, I'm here
on behalf of Wen's Pharmacy

726
00:33:24,350 --> 00:33:26,220
to discuss cooperation with you.

727
00:33:26,430 --> 00:33:28,220
Do you want to sell us the formula,

728
00:33:28,390 --> 00:33:30,330
or to assist in selling your pills?

729
00:33:31,520 --> 00:33:33,370
Not to sell just for Wenshi,

730
00:33:33,670 --> 00:33:35,300
but for Wenshi and Jujing Apothecary.

731
00:33:36,350 --> 00:33:38,890
If Qingshen Pill becomes a hot seller,

732
00:33:38,910 --> 00:33:41,610
it'll boost revenue
and enhance reputation

733
00:33:41,630 --> 00:33:43,090
for both Wen's Pharmacy

734
00:33:43,110 --> 00:33:44,220
and Jujing Apothecary.

735
00:33:44,480 --> 00:33:46,890
Also, it'll prove moderately beneficial

736
00:33:47,190 --> 00:33:48,460
for your grand ambitions.

737
00:33:48,480 --> 00:33:50,410
If we collaborate,

738
00:33:50,560 --> 00:33:52,090
while Wenshi gains onefold benefits,

739
00:33:52,480 --> 00:33:54,060
Jujing Apothecary will secure double.

740
00:33:55,670 --> 00:33:57,330
Frankly, to boost revenue

741
00:33:57,560 --> 00:33:58,540
and enhance reputation,

742
00:33:59,080 --> 00:34:01,220
you should turn
to Tian's Apothecary instead.

743
00:34:05,430 --> 00:34:06,330
Honestly,

744
00:34:06,350 --> 00:34:07,500
as I was heading over here,

745
00:34:07,520 --> 00:34:08,980
I happened to pass by Tian's Apothecary.

746
00:34:09,270 --> 00:34:11,420
But to do business,

747
00:34:11,710 --> 00:34:13,420
I must be capable.

748
00:34:14,110 --> 00:34:17,210
Also I value the character of partners.

749
00:34:22,400 --> 00:34:23,540
I have a meeting coming up soon.

750
00:34:24,590 --> 00:34:25,380
I will certainly consider

751
00:34:25,960 --> 00:34:27,020
your proposal.

752
00:34:27,040 --> 00:34:27,900
Mr. Xia,

753
00:34:28,590 --> 00:34:31,690
I couldn't partner with you in Qizhou.

754
00:34:32,000 --> 00:34:33,900
I hope now in Shanghai,

755
00:34:34,150 --> 00:34:35,770
we can make up for that regret.

756
00:34:41,200 --> 00:34:42,940
[Manager's Office]
I've never met such a discourteous,

757
00:34:43,060 --> 00:34:44,210
rude, and arrogant person!

758
00:34:45,750 --> 00:34:47,210
You're just not worldly enough.

759
00:34:48,710 --> 00:34:50,060
You knew his nature full well

760
00:34:50,230 --> 00:34:51,060
before sending me there.

761
00:34:52,060 --> 00:34:54,500
Merely to subject me to humiliation?

762
00:34:55,500 --> 00:34:56,130
No,

763
00:34:57,230 --> 00:34:58,770
it's just for fun.

764
00:35:06,480 --> 00:35:07,940
I'll go next time. Okay?

765
00:35:08,400 --> 00:35:08,980
Don't bother.

766
00:35:09,670 --> 00:35:11,730
Next time, I'll still take the lead.

767
00:35:11,880 --> 00:35:13,460
I'll make him pay back double

768
00:35:13,480 --> 00:35:14,650
for today's humiliation.

769
00:35:15,080 --> 00:35:15,900
I'm behind you!

770
00:35:16,840 --> 00:35:17,770
Wen's Pharmacy.

771
00:35:19,840 --> 00:35:20,340
Where?

772
00:35:23,110 --> 00:35:23,730
Yes.

773
00:35:29,310 --> 00:35:30,170
Tomorrow?

774
00:35:31,960 --> 00:35:33,250
Okay.

775
00:35:33,960 --> 00:35:34,690
See you tomorrow.

776
00:35:39,040 --> 00:35:40,770
Mr. Mei from Jujing Apothecary called

777
00:35:41,480 --> 00:35:42,730
to invite us to discuss

778
00:35:42,960 --> 00:35:44,770
the cooperation details

779
00:35:45,270 --> 00:35:47,060
for Qingshen Pill tomorrow.

780
00:35:48,750 --> 00:35:49,730
I told them.

781
00:35:50,920 --> 00:35:52,130
You went to Jujing Apothecary?

782
00:35:53,360 --> 00:35:55,130
After leaving Tian's Apothecary

783
00:35:55,150 --> 00:35:55,860
with a sense of reluctance,

784
00:35:56,150 --> 00:35:57,540
I went straight to Jujing Apothecary.

785
00:35:58,880 --> 00:35:59,820
You convinced them?

786
00:36:02,630 --> 00:36:05,380
Anyway,
Mr. Xia said he would consider it.

787
00:36:08,270 --> 00:36:09,130
Xia Yuan?

788
00:36:10,190 --> 00:36:11,130
Did you see him?

789
00:36:11,310 --> 00:36:11,980
Yes.

790
00:36:12,000 --> 00:36:12,820
Do you know him?

791
00:36:14,560 --> 00:36:15,980
Had some dealings with him.

792
00:36:18,310 --> 00:36:18,980
Really?

793
00:36:26,310 --> 00:36:28,460
Mr. Xia is quite mysterious.

794
00:36:28,880 --> 00:36:30,290
Few here have ever seen him.

795
00:36:32,000 --> 00:36:33,210
Did you two…?

796
00:36:37,710 --> 00:36:38,340
What?

797
00:36:39,560 --> 00:36:40,170
Nothing.

798
00:36:41,520 --> 00:36:43,090
Tomorrow at Jujing Apothecary.

799
00:36:44,840 --> 00:36:45,380
Mr. Wen,

800
00:36:45,790 --> 00:36:47,460
why don't you try some Qingshen Pills?

801
00:36:47,840 --> 00:36:48,570
It's settled.

802
00:36:48,750 --> 00:36:49,820
At 4:00 PM tomorrow,

803
00:36:50,040 --> 00:36:51,290
people from Wen's Pharmacy
will come over.

804
00:36:52,310 --> 00:36:52,860
Got it.

805
00:36:53,960 --> 00:36:55,290
Then by 3:00 PM tomorrow,

806
00:36:55,440 --> 00:36:56,170
I need all the information

807
00:36:56,190 --> 00:36:58,060
on Wen Zhiqiu and Wen's Pharmacy.

808
00:36:58,480 --> 00:36:59,130
Got it.

809
00:36:59,880 --> 00:37:00,650
But

810
00:37:01,230 --> 00:37:02,820
are we really going to partner
with them?

811
00:37:04,630 --> 00:37:05,570
Why not?

812
00:37:05,790 --> 00:37:07,610
Over 10 categories
with over 30 varieties

813
00:37:07,750 --> 00:37:09,860
of refreshing prepared medicines

814
00:37:09,880 --> 00:37:10,610
are available in Shanghai.

815
00:37:10,790 --> 00:37:11,860
And the best seller

816
00:37:11,880 --> 00:37:14,020
is Tian's Apothecary's
Western Bunao Pill,

817
00:37:14,230 --> 00:37:15,570
accounting for about 80%
of the market share.

818
00:37:15,790 --> 00:37:16,730
Generally speaking,

819
00:37:17,040 --> 00:37:19,420
once a prepared medicine occupies
over 50% of the market share,

820
00:37:19,710 --> 00:37:21,290
a later entrant will find it hard
to break through.

821
00:37:23,000 --> 00:37:25,500
But what if its efficacy is comparable,

822
00:37:26,310 --> 00:37:28,340
yet it has lower cost and price?

823
00:37:28,560 --> 00:37:29,900
We promoted several prepared medicines

824
00:37:29,920 --> 00:37:31,420
that sold well in the north,

825
00:37:31,750 --> 00:37:33,060
with competitive pricing.

826
00:37:33,230 --> 00:37:34,650
However, some failed to adapt
to the local market

827
00:37:35,040 --> 00:37:37,730
while others were strongly blocked
by Tian's Apothecary.

828
00:37:37,880 --> 00:37:39,540
None managed to gain traction here.

829
00:37:41,000 --> 00:37:41,820
So I want

830
00:37:42,960 --> 00:37:45,090
to partner
with local Shanghai apothecaries

831
00:37:45,400 --> 00:37:47,090
to see if we can adapt
to the local market.

832
00:37:48,270 --> 00:37:50,540
But Wen's Pharmacy is simply too weak

833
00:37:50,710 --> 00:37:52,540
to stand up to Tian's Apothecary.

834
00:37:53,540 --> 00:37:54,540
You're absolutely right.

835
00:37:55,380 --> 00:37:57,090
Wen's Pharmacy is very weak.

836
00:37:57,710 --> 00:37:59,570
But it has one major advantage.

837
00:37:59,920 --> 00:38:00,460
What is it?

838
00:38:07,110 --> 00:38:07,730
By the way,

839
00:38:09,230 --> 00:38:10,500
have any of your classmates

840
00:38:11,020 --> 00:38:12,170
heard from Xia Chu?

841
00:38:12,190 --> 00:38:13,090
No lately.

842
00:38:16,270 --> 00:38:18,340
It's been ages since he last wrote home.

843
00:38:20,270 --> 00:38:21,730
I wonder

844
00:38:23,080 --> 00:38:23,900
how he's doing in France.

845
00:38:24,460 --> 00:38:26,660
[Tian's Apothecary]

846
00:38:30,460 --> 00:38:33,140
[Jujing Apothecary]

847
00:38:34,880 --> 00:38:36,090
I must remind you.

848
00:38:36,110 --> 00:38:37,650
Xia Yuan is meticulous,

849
00:38:37,670 --> 00:38:38,690
shrewd and resolute.

850
00:38:38,920 --> 00:38:39,900
If you negotiate with him,

851
00:38:39,920 --> 00:38:41,730
you must be on high alert.

852
00:38:41,750 --> 00:38:42,690
Rest assured.

853
00:38:43,520 --> 00:38:45,610
Have you figured out how to negotiate?

854
00:38:45,920 --> 00:38:47,020
Just take what's there.

855
00:38:47,640 --> 00:38:48,130
Take this.

856
00:38:49,020 --> 00:38:49,540
Let's go.

857
00:39:01,940 --> 00:39:02,610
My coat.

858
00:39:08,190 --> 00:39:10,730
