864
00:39:41,190 --> 00:39:42,650
How cheap is this!

865
00:39:45,150 --> 00:39:47,210
Why can't they outsell Tian's Apothecary
across the street?

866
00:39:47,230 --> 00:39:48,940
Please stop talking nonsense.

867
00:39:48,960 --> 00:39:50,340
What I said is the truth!

868
00:39:50,500 --> 00:39:51,770
You're on their turf right now.

869
00:39:51,790 --> 00:39:53,090
Can't speak like that here.

870
00:39:53,580 --> 00:39:55,250
We'll talk with them shortly.

871
00:39:55,270 --> 00:39:56,770
This is meant to be a show
of force first.

872
00:39:57,580 --> 00:39:58,340
But you…

873
00:39:59,310 --> 00:40:00,090
Mr. Mei.

874
00:40:00,460 --> 00:40:01,170
Ms. Chu.

875
00:40:01,790 --> 00:40:02,500
Mr. Mei,

876
00:40:02,630 --> 00:40:04,250
this is Mr. Wen Zhiqiu,

877
00:40:04,270 --> 00:40:05,690
Chairman and General Manager

878
00:40:05,790 --> 00:40:06,860
of Wen's Pharmacy.

879
00:40:07,110 --> 00:40:08,570
This is Mr. Mei from Jujing Apothecary.

880
00:40:09,710 --> 00:40:10,380
Hello.

881
00:40:11,140 --> 00:40:11,690
Hello.

882
00:40:12,060 --> 00:40:12,650
