883
00:40:13,120 --> 00:40:13,770
Upstairs, please.

884
00:40:27,600 --> 00:40:28,540
We'll sell such Renshen

885
00:40:28,660 --> 00:40:29,900
for just a few hundred silver dollars.

886
00:40:31,790 --> 00:40:32,980
But here, it barely qualifies

887
00:40:33,160 --> 00:40:34,290
as third-tier,

888
00:40:34,750 --> 00:40:36,420
worth around a thousand at best.

889
00:40:36,750 --> 00:40:37,420
Please.

890
00:40:39,060 --> 00:40:41,730
I happen to have a copy
of this painting.

891
00:40:42,710 --> 00:40:44,060
Mine's just newer.

892
00:40:44,630 --> 00:40:47,060
I only paid 3 silver dollars for it.

893
00:40:47,500 --> 00:40:48,540
How much did you pay?

894
00:40:49,150 --> 00:40:50,340
This Old Tree and Cold Crows

895
00:40:50,380 --> 00:40:52,060
is an authentic work by Zhao Boju
of the Southern Song Dynasty.

896
00:40:52,420 --> 00:40:52,860
Who?

897
00:40:53,100 --> 00:40:55,020
Zhao Boju of the Southern Song Dynasty.

898
00:40:55,750 --> 00:40:57,650
I don't know how much

899
00:40:57,670 --> 00:40:58,460
Mr. Xia paid for it.

900
00:40:59,230 --> 00:41:00,730
All I know is some collector

901
00:41:01,060 --> 00:41:02,290
offered 20,000 silver dollars,

902
00:41:03,100 --> 00:41:04,210
but Mr. Xia wouldn't sell.

903
00:41:07,120 --> 00:41:08,060
If I were him, I'd have sold it!

904
00:41:12,270 --> 00:41:14,250
Ms. Chu, please have a seat.

905
00:41:14,500 --> 00:41:15,090
Very well.

906
00:41:21,580 --> 00:41:22,540
Please try

907
00:41:23,190 --> 00:41:24,210
