914
00:41:39,540 --> 00:41:40,220
Tastes great.

915
00:41:41,180 --> 00:41:41,980
Mr. Xia is here.

916
00:41:42,940 --> 00:41:43,660
Then it's settled.

917
00:41:44,060 --> 00:41:46,100
