918
00:41:46,580 --> 00:41:47,260
Alright.

919
00:41:47,280 --> 00:41:48,260
See you.

920
00:41:48,260 --> 00:41:48,900
Take care.

921
00:41:49,360 --> 00:41:50,060
Please.

922
00:41:53,520 --> 00:41:54,300
Hello, Shaohua.

923
00:41:54,520 --> 00:41:55,140
Mr. Xia.

924
00:41:55,260 --> 00:41:55,700
